{"tid":2413229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"節目《香港病了》改名做《疫行者》 　港台：因為正月","createTime":"2021-02-18T14:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T14:43:42.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7701c8dd503e2a51e8cd2f2a018b2055cace3ed","tid":2413229,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n早排該台原本有個節目叫《香港故事-香港病了》，訪問咗《十年．自焚者》導演周冠威，內容係講反修例運動，點知成個節目要押後至嚟緊周日播出，首集最終不單未能以周冠威做打頭陣，最新「打壓」港台招數係要求節目都要改名，個節目最新名叫做《香港故事-疫行者》。<br />\n港台回覆話，因為仍在正月期間，所以呢個節目易名為《香港故事-疫行者》，即係「香港病了」四粒字唔見咗，可能嫌「香港病了」唔吉利？港台網頁亦已更新；由於改名，連最初的宣傳片、Facebook宣傳都要一併刪走。<br />\n<br />\n首集改訪問風水師<br />\n節目首集梗係冇咗《十年》導演之一周冠威啦，改以訪問風水命理師，<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/AZWTLK3OAFBBPADTWMP3WDUGHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FAZWTLK3OAFBBPADTWMP3WDUGHQ%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Bd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=d60db7d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FAZWTLK3OAFBBPADTWMP3WDUGHQ%2F&h=2cb1ab90\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/AZWTLK3OAFBBPADTWMP3WDUGHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n港台報道，梁今早於一個內部會議上回應員工質詢時稱，停播BBC新聞節目的決定由他作出，他沒受到來自政府高層的壓力，亦稱有關決定與處理新聞編採無關。報道續稱，梁當時解釋國家廣電總局所作出的決定適用於全國；香港屬中國境內，港台亦是政府部門。<br />\n<br />\n港台工會憂成壞先例 削公眾了解國際渠道<br />\n港台節目製作人員工會其後發聲明指，對梁以非公開方式向公眾解釋決定感到遺憾及不解。工會續表示，在一國兩制下，以往未見香港跟隨廣電局的決定，認為梁此舉「恐怕反應過度」，令人憂慮會成先例，客觀效果上亦令公眾減少了解國際資訊的渠道。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/CCKIHOOUNRD3LB6VETRCAZPWBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FCCKIHOOUNRD3LB6VETRCAZPWBQ%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Bd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=fb64cf40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210218%2FCCKIHOOUNRD3LB6VETRCAZPWBQ%2F&h=e42985ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210218/CCKIHOOUNRD3LB6VETRCAZPWBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f3f95b9036b0ba2de246e8c3196a7982ba488d0b","tid":2413229,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"香港屬中國境內<br />\n<br />\n香港係國内境外喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236be645d0bb08e765e401f53fbbbcc83bd8c9ed","tid":2413229,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f95b9036b0ba2de246e8c3196a7982ba488d0b","tid":2413229,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"香港屬中國境內<br />\n<br />\n香港係國内境外喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"做奴才做到自宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n殘體注意<br />\n<br />\n境外，是指中国边境（国界）以外的所有国家与地区和中国以内政府尚未实施行政管辖的地域；境外范围包括：港澳台和其他外国国家和地区。[1]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/境外/9040378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%2F9040378&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69Bd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=844b3f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/境外/9040378</a>"}]}